          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y00A85AJ-line-1" n="1">Thus spoke great <hi rend="italics">Bedell</hi> from his tomb,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y00A85AJ-line-2" n="2">Mortal! I would not change my doom,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y00A85AJ-line-3" n="3">To live in such a restless state;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y00A85AJ-line-4" n="4">To be unfortunately great;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y00A85AJ-line-5" n="5">To pity fools; to spurn at knaves;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y00A85AJ-line-6" n="6">To shine among a race of slaves;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y00A85AJ-line-7" n="7">To learn from wise men to complain,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y00A85AJ-line-8" n="8">And only rise to fall again:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y00A85AJ-line-9" n="9">No──── let my dusty relics rest,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y00A85AJ-line-10" n="10">Till I shall rise amongst the blest.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </body>
